text: Zvenyhorod () mean villages in the Western Ukraine. Zvenyhorod may also refer to: * Zvenyhorod - in Pustomyty Raion, Lviv Oblast. It was the former capital of the Principality of Zvenyhorod * Zvenyhorod, Borshchiv Raion - in Borshchiv Raion * Zvenyhorod, Buchach Raion - in Buchach Raion, Ternopil Oblast
title: Zvenyhorod (disambiguation)
